Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), python3-all, dh-python
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/lenik/pyname
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: pyname
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-pypinyin, python3-jieba
Description: Pinyin utilities for filenames with Chinese characters
 pyname provides command-line utilities for working with Chinese characters
 in filenames:
 .
  - test-zh: Check if filenames contain Chinese characters
  - pinyinize: Convert Chinese text to pinyin (like echo)
  - ren2py: Rename files containing Chinese characters to pinyin

